<h1 class="hero-h">The 2026 state of <em>AI-native GTM.</em></h1>
<p class="hero-sub">An annual synthesis from Treetop Growth Strategy on how B2B revenue motions are being rebuilt for the AI era. The seven shifts that matter, the maturity stages we observe at mid-market, what 2026 validated, what it killed, and the seven specific bets we are willing to put on 2027. Built for CEOs, investors, fractional operators, and analysts who want a citable read.</p>
</div></div>

